query: SELECT id, name, fileUrl FROM documents WHERE (category='other' OR category='booking') AND (fileUrl LIKE '%.jpg' OR fileUrl LIKE '%.jpeg' OR fileUrl LIKE '%.png' OR fileUrl LIKE '%.webp' OR fileUrl LIKE '%.JPG' OR fileUrl LIKE '%.JPEG' OR fileUrl LIKE '%.PNG') AND name NOT LIKE '%parking%' ORDER BY name;
